        <updateDate>2021-08-16T12:00:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Terrorism Reporting And Classifying Act of 2019 or the TRAC Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a federal interagency working group to coordinate the collection and reporting of federal data related to domestic terrorism incidents.</p> <p>The bill directs the working group to establish a standard interpretation of the term<em> domestic terrorism</em>, develop a federal database for storing information and data related to domestic terrorism incidents, and report on domestic terrorism incidents. <br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
